ith all Customs requirements. Should Customs choose to examine your merchandise and determine that it is eligible for duty free benefits then you may be fined and your shipments delayed.\r\n\r\nTo mitigate this risk and to provide evidence of a rigorous due diligence process, Omega experts verify from where your supplier is manufacturing your merchandise as well as procuring the relevant raw materials.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Auditing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-26 07:25:33', '2015-08-26 15:25:33', '', 32, 'http://local.omega.com/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
