(97, 1, '2015-08-30 23:40:30', '2015-08-31 07:40:30', '<h1>About us</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Every day many of the world''s most trusted consumer brands put their faith in Omega to ensure the integrity of their global supply chains as they endeavor to work with partners who are secure, reliable, ethical and free from corrupt practices.</p>\r\nOmega goes beyond monitoring. We focus upon complete inspections, thorough investigations, full disclosure and effective remediation. We strive to ensure that all parties, from manufacturers, trading entities, logistics providers and brands have full transparency over their product, supply chain partners, employees and associates. We enable our clients to understand any shortcomings then provide them with the expertise to remediate effectively allowing them to operate their supply chains with complete confidence.', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-30 23:40:30', '2015-08-31 07:40:30', '', 8, 'http://local.omega.com/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
