(126, 1, '2015-09-07 20:01:47', '2015-09-08 04:01:47', '<h1>Anti-Corruption</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Fraud and corruption across supply chains is a serious risk and has enormous potential consequences to your business. Common corrupt practices include purchase orders being awarded to poorly qualified suppliers, factories with egregious ethical issues becoming part of your supply chain or defective shipments being passed by quality inspectors.</p>\r\nWhile these risks can never be eliminated it is imperative that you have the requisite controls in place across your business operations. Omega‚Äôs dedicated ethical monitoring team provides a broad range of integrity investigations services, such as conflicts of interest, bribery, and fraud, both internal and external, to companies who may not have the in-house resources to manage this risk themselves. Omega has unparalleled experience in developing and managing anti-corruption programs, programs which span more than 20 countries and a supply base in excess of 2,000 manufacturers.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Anti-Corruption', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:01:47', '2015-09-08 04:01:47', '', 41, 'http://local.omega.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:04', '2015-09-08 04:02:04', '', 'banner_auditing_desktop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_auditing_desktop', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:04', '2015-09-08 04:02:04', '', 32, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_auditing_desktop.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(128, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:09', '2015-09-08 04:02:09', '', 'banner_auditing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_auditing', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:09', '2015-09-08 04:02:09', '', 32, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_auditing.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(129, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:12', '2015-09-08 04:02:12', '<h1>AUDITING</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Omega''s auditors assess your supply chain partners against proprietary, international and local regulations. Our service is flexible; we can just as simply adopt a proprietary standard as we can develop one in line with your precise requirements.</p>\r\nOffering a full spectrum of supply chain auditing services, Omega''s dedicated teams of professionals, expert in their specific disciplines and local to the markets in which they operate, provide many of the world''s best known brands and retailers with eyes and ears in the field.\r\n\r\nOmega''s audit methodology is developed from our unparalleled experience in handling industry best practices within a multitude of product types from around the world.\r\n<h2>Social Compliance</h2>\r\nAn industry leader in the social compliance field, Omega performs more than 3,000 social compliance audits annually across China, South Asia, South East Asia, and The Middle East. Representing many of the world''s most ethical companies, Omega provides a window into the working conditions across their global manufacturing base enabling our partners to make critical business decisions in complete confidence.\r\n\r\nHeadquartered in the heart of Asia, Omega understands that each market is different. Omega invests heavily in its auditing teams who are vastly knowledgeable, highly experienced, expert in international and local regulations as well as native in the requisite language(s) of their market. We are highly sensitive to local cultures and perform audits as sensitively as possible without disrupting your supplier relationships.\r\n\r\nOmega understands that the most daunting challenge your manufacturers face is not in understanding where their problems lie, but in how to resolve them efficiently and effectively. A different formula is needed. Omega is set apart from its competitors by a focus on corrective action planning and supplier remediation. Omega''s approach is centered upon a real knowledge of the challenges, clear communications, a detailed corrective action plan agreed onsite and practical advice each step of the way.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.\r\n<h2>SUPPLY CHAIN SECURITY</h2>\r\nIn order to demonstrate compliance with international supply chain security standards, importers must continually assess their supply chains to identify, mitigate and eliminate potential security hazards as well as monitor ongoing improvements. Failure to comply with importer security requirements, such as C-TPAT and PIP, may result in Customs delaying your shipments or even having them seized at enormous cost to your business.\r\n\r\nOmega is an industry leader in the supply chain security field. We are expert at working with all supply chain partners, from manufacturers, warehouses, logistics providers to ports and perform in excess of 1,000 security audits each year across more than 20 countries worldwide. Omega has world-class account management experience; developing risk analyses and managing global supply chain security programs for some of the most prestigious importers into the United States and Canada.\r\n\r\nYour supply chain is more complicated than you might think. With a wide network of suppliers, some large, some small, some experienced and some new, spread over many countries, effectively assuring a secure and compliant supply chain is a daunting challenge. Omega''s security expertise will guide you.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.\r\n<h2>COUNTRY OF ORIGIN DUE DILIGENCE</h2>\r\nShould your company be benefitting from reduced tariffs under the benefits of specific free trade agreements (FTAs), such as the arrangement between The EU and ASEAN, it is imperative that your merchandise is in compliance with all Customs requirements. Should Customs choose to examine your merchandise and determine that it is eligible for duty free benefits then you may be fined and your shipments delayed.\r\n\r\nTo mitigate this risk and to provide evidence of a rigorous due diligence process, Omega experts verify from where your supplier is manufacturing your merchandise as well as procuring the relevant raw materials.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Auditing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:12', '2015-09-08 04:02:12', '', 32, 'http://local.omega.com/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(130, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:27', '2015-09-08 04:02:27', '', 'banner_inspection_desktop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_inspection_desktop', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:27', '2015-09-08 04:02:27', '', 39, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_inspection_desktop.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(131, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:31', '2015-09-08 04:02:31', '', 'banner_inspection', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_inspection', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:31', '2015-09-08 04:02:31', '', 39, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_inspection.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(132, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:35', '2015-09-08 04:02:35', '<h1>Inspections</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Relying on in-house factory inspections can be a risk. Too often merchandise received is of inferior quality, incorrectly packaged, incorrectly labeled or short shipped.</p>\r\nWith supply chains stretching across the globe, the time required to return the merchandise, process a claim and allow vendors to rework orders can cost significant retail dollars.\r\n\r\nOmega provides you with comprehensive quality inspection services. Our 3rd party inspection teams are on the front line, working at your manufacturers, striving to assure that the goods you receive meet your exacting requirements.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Inspections', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:35', '2015-09-08 04:02:35', '', 39, 'http://local.omega.com/39-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(133, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:52', '2015-09-08 04:02:52', '', 'banner_training_desktop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_training_desktop', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:52', '2015-09-08 04:02:52', '', 43, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_training_desktop.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(134, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:56', '2015-09-08 04:02:56', '', 'banner_training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'banner_training', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:56', '2015-09-08 04:02:56', '', 43, 'http://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/banner_training.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(135, 1, '2015-09-07 20:02:59', '2015-09-08 04:02:59', '<h1>Training</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Achieving security and social compliance across a vast production network is a unique challenge. With factory security criteria under development and social compliance standards numerous, complicated and subject to change, many of your vendors are in need of guidance.</p>\r\nLeveraging our extensive remediation expertise, we operate our own proprietary training programs in which our expert social compliance and factory security teams will educate your vendors in the requisite procedures to ensure minimum standards are met.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="http://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:59', '2015-09-08 04:02:59', '', 43, 'http://local.omega.com/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
